gridworld.grid

Class UnboundedGrid<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • gridworld.grid.AbstractGrid<E>
      • gridworld.grid.UnboundedGrid<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Grid<E>

    public class UnboundedGrid<E>
extends AbstractGrid<E>
    An UnboundedGrid is a rectangular grid with an unbounded number of rows and columns.
    The implementation of this class is testable on the AP CS AB exam.
